  • public class EldDriverBehaviorRecord
extends EldBroadcast
    Class containing data from Driver Behavior broadcast messages.

     Parameters:
  - Cruise Control Speed      (km/h)
  - Cruise Control Status     (see EldDriverCruiseStates)
  - Throttle Position         (%)
  - Accelerator Position      (%)
  - Brake Position            (%)
  - Seat Belt Status          (see EldDriverSeatBeltStates)
  - Steering Wheel Angle      (degree)
  - ABS status                (see EldDriverAbsStates)
  - Traction Status           (see EldDriverTractionStates)
  - Stability Status          (see EldDriverStabilityStates)
  - Brake System Pressure     (kPa)
